'''亞美尼亞－土耳其關係'''（{{lang-tr|Ermenistan-Türkiye ilişkileri}}、{{lang-hy|Հայ-թուրքական հարաբերություններ}}）是指亚美尼亚与土耳其历史上及现代的双边关系。<ref name=establish>{{Cite news |first=Sebnem |last=Arsu |title=Turkey and Armenia to Establish Diplomatic Ties |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/01/world/europe/01armenia.html?_r=1&hp |quote=Turkey and Armenia, whose century of hostilities constitutes one of the world's most enduring and acrimonious international rivalries, have agreed to establish diplomatic relations |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=August 31, 2009 |access-date=2009-09-01 |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219102130/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/01/world/europe/01armenia.html?_r=1&hp }}</ref>两国尚未建交，但亚美尼亚在土耳其第一大城市[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]设有[[實質大使館|具大使館功能]]的代表機構。<ref>{{cite web |title=BSEC |url=https://www.mfa.am/en/in-international-organizations/95 |website=亚美尼亚外交部 |accessdate=2022-03-08 |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308041117/https://www.mfa.am/en/in-international-organizations/95 }}</ref>

== 历史概况 ==

1991年9月，[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]宣布獨立後不久，[[土耳其|土耳其]]就承認了亞美尼亞的主權，但亚美尼亚因为1915年[[奧斯曼帝國|奧斯曼帝國]]土耳其民族主義者發動的[[亞美尼亞種族大屠殺|亞美尼亞種族大屠殺]]的[[對亞美尼亞種族大屠殺的承認|歷史認知]]問題與[[土耳其|土耳其]]之間有外交上和對大屠殺事件承認問題上存在爭議，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.europarl.europa.eu/sides/getDoc.do?type=IM-PRESS&reference=20060922IPR10896&language=EN|title=European Parliament critical of slowdown in Turkey's reform process|language=en|publisher=|accessdate=2015-12-02|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002154536/http://www.europarl.europa.eu/sides/getDoc.do?language=EN&type=IM-PRESS&reference=20060922IPR10896|dead-url=no}}</ref>未能建立[[外交關係|外交關係]]，亚美尼亚与[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]一样，是世界上极少数未与土耳其建立外交关系的国家。而土耳其历来在[[納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]期间支持[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]，并關閉了與亞美尼亞的邊界。[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]期间，土耳其更是支持[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]捍衛自己的領土<ref>{{Cite web|title=土耳其支持阿塞拜疆捍卫自己的领土|work=TRT中文|url=https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/09/28/tu-er-qi-zhi-chi-a-sai-bai-jiang-han-wei-zi-ji-de-ling-tu-1498722|accessdate=2020-09-29|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120162446/https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/09/28/tu-er-qi-zhi-chi-a-sai-bai-jiang-han-wei-zi-ji-de-ling-tu-1498722|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並譴責亞美尼亞對阿塞拜疆的襲擊<ref>{{Cite web|title=土耳其强烈谴责亚美尼亚袭击阿塞拜疆 {{!}} TRT 中文|url=https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/09/27/tu-er-qi-qiang-lie-qian-ze-ya-mei-ni-ya-xi-ji-a-sai-bai-jiang-1497965|accessdate=2020-09-29|work=www.trt.net.tr|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161446/https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/09/27/tu-er-qi-qiang-lie-qian-ze-ya-mei-ni-ya-xi-ji-a-sai-bai-jiang-1497965|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在停戰協議簽署後，土耳其聲稱亞塞拜然取得了「歷史性的勝利」並祝賀亞塞拜然成功奪回故土。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Azerbaijan gained historic victory - Turkish government|url=https://www.azernews.az/nation/172448.html|accessdate=2020-11-11|date=2020-11-10|work=AzerNews.az|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161506/https://www.azernews.az/nation/172448.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

尽管如此，近年亞土雙方已透過元首互訪等方式逐漸修復關係、重建溝通對話。2022年，两国关系进一步正常化，往返[[埃里温|埃里温]]与伊斯坦布尔的航班在中断两年后恢复起飞。而土耳其外长梅夫吕特·恰武什奥卢也表示土耳其外交部邀请了亚美尼亚官员参加3月11日至13日举行的第二届[[安塔利亚|安塔利亚]]外交论坛。<ref>{{cite web |title=土耳其与亚美尼亚继续努力实现关系正常化 |url=https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1723009321600429960&wfr=spider&for=pc |website=[[土耳其驻华大使馆|土耳其驻华大使馆]] |accessdate=2022-01-26}}</ref>

现今，有4万至7万名亚美尼亚人在[[土耳其|土耳其]]居住，主要集中在伊斯坦布尔及周边地区<ref>{{cite web |last=Turay |first=Anna |title=Tarihte Ermeniler |publisher=Bolsohays:Istanbul Armenians Like many other ethnicities [[亚美尼亚裔印度人|亚美尼亚裔印度人]] too have played a role historically and had an impact historically. Today however the community has been reduced to about a hundred living in Kolkata |url=http://www.bolsohays.com/webac.asp?referans=1 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209171028/http://www.bolsohays.com/webac.asp?referans=1 |archivedate=2008-02-09 |accessdate=2007-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

